<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I think it makes more sense. You would understand better the main character&apos;s behavior and feelings if you read Dissolution. Moreover, there are refer<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I think it makes more sense. You would understand better the main character's behavior and feelings if you read Dissolution. Moreover, there are references to the the 1st installment. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
